{"tid":2438511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(大件事！)教宗晤伊斯蘭教什葉派最高領袖","createTime":"2021-03-08T14:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T01:59:30.000Z","uid":54930,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"2385feb0c6fd772f7d8ff7424f78cd207f5a91cb","tid":2438511,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"教宗晤伊拉克什葉派最高領袖　強調不同宗教合作重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sOhdOHuzOh7yMRIOaFlpsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMzNy4xNTYxNzcxNTYxNzcxNA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/G_yOf5JjMaMSwBGL7qbN1Q--~B/aD00NTI7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/ctwant_com_582/675e61ddda0fd15729620de4c67c66fc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsOhdOHuzOh7yMRIOaFlpsw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMzNy4xNTYxNzcxNTYxNzcxNA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FG_yOf5JjMaMSwBGL7qbN1Q--~B%2FaD00NTI7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fctwant_com_582%2F675e61ddda0fd15729620de4c67c66fc&h=995b21d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正在伊拉克訪問的教宗方濟各在南部伊斯蘭教什葉派聖城納傑夫，與當地什葉派最高領袖西斯塔尼，歷史性會面大約50分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n西斯塔尼感謝方濟各到訪，表明伊拉克的基督信仰者與所有伊拉克人一樣，應該生活在和平與安全中，並充份享有與其他伊拉克人民相同的權利。<br />\n<br />\n方濟各感謝西斯塔尼，表達捍衛最弱小和最受迫害人民的聲音，又強調不同宗教合作與友誼的重要性，透過互相尊重和對話，為伊拉克作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n在與西斯塔尼會談後，方濟各到南部烏爾古城遺址，出席不同信仰的對話會議，呼籲各派放低仇恨，為和平團結努力。"},{"pid":"4697960ce06907972160c2f734a70c173dd93947","tid":2438511,"uid":377617,"like":4,"dislike":37,"score":-33,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"什葉派好人教派黎<br />\n<br />\n遜尼派先係壞人"},{"pid":"97aa1d75f63dcdfd26e4d2fbabf83b58c0cb8476","tid":2438511,"uid":79793,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"一齊呃傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錢齊齊搵，有幼齊齊搞"},{"pid":"c579cce3dce5d345c94170fd7143428af1e22101","tid":2438511,"uid":300263,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"根本大家都係猶太教分支嚟，歸根究底信緊同一個神/天主/真神/上帝，撈埋一碟算啦不如"},{"pid":"56bb064c2df7e4fccbeca1a4dbebf0561288e5a8","tid":2438511,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"兩個教打咗成千年仗，宜家話和好就和好，咁將一千年嚟嘅血汗恩仇置於何物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5043cb492c297fef03ed8c8f8d21d59f3a97bf","tid":2438511,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"Jesus ala<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09a0bf528394e2ec4c1fd5cef8f613736d67bea","tid":2438511,"uid":63669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrdxgqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrdxgqA.jpg&h=17129c0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6b76671e9e4e674d356bbf9ebe90d36d3487c80","tid":2438511,"uid":112232,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"cite